パッケージ xyz.mlserver.reflectionhelper.annotation

注釈型 Method

  • @Target(FIELD)
@Retention(RUNTIME)
public @interface Method
    Resolves the annotated MethodWrapper or Method field to the first matching method name.

    • 必須要素の概要

      必須要素 
      修飾子とタイプ 必須要素 説明
      String className
      Name of the class to load this method from
      String[] value
      Possible names of the method.

    • 任意要素の概要

      任意要素 
      修飾子とタイプ 任意要素 説明
      boolean ignoreExceptions
      Whether to ignore any reflection exceptions thrown.
      Minecraft.Version[] versions
      Specific versions for the names.

    • 要素の詳細

      • className

        String className
        Name of the class to load this method from
        戻り値:
        name of the class

      • value

        String[] value
        Possible names of the method. Use > or < as a name prefix in combination with versions() to specify versions newer- or older-than.
        戻り値:
        method names

      • versions

        Minecraft.Version[] versions
        Specific versions for the names.
        戻り値:
        Array of versions for the class names
        デフォルト:
        {}

      • ignoreExceptions

        boolean ignoreExceptions
        Whether to ignore any reflection exceptions thrown. Defaults to true
        戻り値:
        whether to ignore exceptions
        デフォルト:
        true
